verbose_text: Expression levels of nine imprinted genes [H19, Ubiquitin protein ligase E3A (UBE3A), Pleckstrin homology like domain family A member 2 (PHLDA2), Cyclin dependent kinase inhibitor 1C (CDKN1C), Tumor protein p 73 (TP73), GNAS complex locus (GNAS), Homeobox protein DLX-5 (DLX5), Probable phospholipid transporting ATPase VA (ATP10A) and Solute carrier family 22 member 18 (SLC22A18)] predominantly expressed from the maternal allele were similar to those of previously reported rhesus PESCs, rPESC-2 and IVF derived ORMES-22.
evidence: Expression levels of nine imprinted genes [H19, Ubiquitin protein ligase E3A (UBE3A), Pleckstrin homology-like domain family A member 2 (PHLDA2), Cyclin-dependent kinase inhibitor 1C (CDKN1C), Tumor protein p 73 (TP73), GNAS complex locus (GNAS), Homeobox protein DLX-5 (DLX5), Probable phospholipid-transporting ATPase VA (ATP10A) and Solute carrier family 22 member 18 (SLC22A18)] predominantly expressed from the maternal allele were similar to those of previously reported rhesus PESCs, rPESC-2               and IVF-derived ORMES-22
